<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>Mystic-Type</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Multiplayer<sp/>R-Type-like<sp/>with<sp/>an<sp/>authoritative<sp/>TCP/UDP<sp/>server<sp/>and<sp/>a<sp/>raylib<sp/>graphical<sp/>client.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>Prerequisites</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>CMake<sp/>≥<sp/>3.14</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>C++17<sp/>compiler</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>raylib<sp/>(fetched<sp/>automatically<sp/>via<sp/>FetchContent)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>Works<sp/>on<sp/>macOS,<sp/>Linux,<sp/>and<sp/>Windows<sp/>(WSA<sp/>init<sp/>handled<sp/>in<sp/>entry<sp/>points).</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
